1
00:00:23,540 --> 00:00:28,450
♪Like a flock of birds
pressing ever forward♪

2
00:00:28,980 --> 00:00:33,350
♪Stranded on an island
shrouded in heavy mist♪

3
00:00:34,450 --> 00:00:38,410
♪We may seem small
beneath the vast world♪

4
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:43,680
♪But not once have we felt despair♪

5
00:00:43,970 --> 00:00:46,770
♪We've crossed waves
a thousand layers deep♪

6
00:00:46,770 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Stepped on reefs hidden in the dark♪

7
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:54,730
♪Facing sharper winds head-on♪

8
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:57,660
♪Our wounds now stitched
into battle robes♪

9
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:00,370
♪The long night
is branded by starlight♪

10
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:05,440
♪We embrace this deep blue together♪

11
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:10,620
♪At the edge of the vast unknown,
I remain unchanged♪

12
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:16,540
♪Holding fast with lonely courage,
roaring without fear♪

13
00:01:16,670 --> 00:01:21,850
♪Determined to be
both my friend and my rival♪

14
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:27,030
♪No one dares to blindly
urge me to turn back♪

15
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:32,090
♪I choose what I believe is worth it♪

16
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:38,340
=Rose and Gun=

17
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:40,980
=Episode 4=

18
00:01:42,010 --> 00:01:42,690
Captain.

19
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,520
Am I the worst soldier you've trained?

20
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:50,360
I've never trained bad soldiers.

21
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,490
You aren't bad.

22
00:01:52,915 --> 00:01:54,960
You are just not being placed
in the right position.

23
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,410
Do you know

24
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,915
what I saw in you when I picked you?

25
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:03,410
You are bold,

26
00:02:03,410 --> 00:02:04,690
tough,

27
00:02:04,690 --> 00:02:06,290
and have adaptability and endurance

28
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:07,290
that surpass your age.

29
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:09,530
These traits are rare
among my new recruits.

30
00:02:10,010 --> 00:02:11,130
For all these years,

31
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,970
I've only seen it in Cheng Yuan.

32
00:02:13,493 --> 00:02:15,880
Sergeant Cheng is a marksman.
I can't be compared to him.

33
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:18,040
He didn't start out as one.

34
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,370
He has gone all the way

35
00:02:19,690 --> 00:02:20,720
to the international level

36
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,250
one shot and one step at a time.

37
00:02:22,271 --> 00:02:23,300
(People's Liberation Army, Navy)

38
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:39,290
Actually,
I've heard about Sergeant Cheng

39
00:02:39,290 --> 00:02:40,880
before joining Blue Blade.

40
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,880
He is the only ace sniper in our brigade

41
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,850
who has won the Tai'e Sword
in many years.

42
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:46,160
Do you want to know

43
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,370
what the ace sniper

44
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:48,640
says about you?

45
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,690
He said
you have a high sense of awareness

46
00:02:52,690 --> 00:02:53,640
and reaction.

47
00:02:53,810 --> 00:02:54,880
You've exceeded everyone

48
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,871
in terms of
your ability to capture information.

49
00:02:57,690 --> 00:02:58,600
However,

50
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:00,810
you are not steady enough.

51
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,250
Captain!

52
00:03:12,530 --> 00:03:13,530
I understand now.

53
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,026
I want to stay on the Blue Blade

54
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:17,093
and become an ace sniper
just like Sergeant Cheng!

55
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:21,410
It's a good thing to be determined

56
00:03:21,690 --> 00:03:24,090
but a soldier speaks with his actions.

57
00:03:24,170 --> 00:03:25,440
If you want to join Blue Blade,

58
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,010
you need to learn many things

59
00:03:27,010 --> 00:03:28,160
to make up for your weaknesses

60
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,250
and show your strengths.

61
00:03:29,290 --> 00:03:30,720
You and your gun must be steady.

62
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,226
That includes your mentality as well.

63
00:03:32,248 --> 00:03:32,850
Understand?

64
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:33,410
Yes, Sir!

65
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:37,410
♪When I speak with the sky♪

66
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:42,280
♪Asking myself about my thoughts♪

67
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,290
Report!

68
00:03:45,290 --> 00:03:47,010
Yi Nanwang, diving preparation complete!

69
00:03:47,010 --> 00:03:47,690
Dive!

70
00:03:47,690 --> 00:03:51,260
♪Do you still dare depart?♪

71
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:54,120
♪As if being pushed
into an unknown whirlpool♪

72
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,340
♪Dangers keep appearing
before your eyes♪

73
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:58,690
♪We shout with bodies full of scars♪

74
00:03:58,690 --> 00:04:00,620
♪We resist our internal struggles♪

75
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:04,670
♪In the surging waves♪

76
00:04:04,890 --> 00:04:08,920
♪It's a confrontation
between courage and pain♪

77
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:13,050
♪Enter the ocean with my whole life♪

78
00:04:13,130 --> 00:04:14,600
When treading water,

79
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:17,840
use leg movements
similar to the breaststroke kick.

80
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:19,280
However,

81
00:04:19,520 --> 00:04:22,320
the draw-in and kick-out range
should be slightly smaller.

82
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,730
Once in the water,

83
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:27,200
stay vertical to the water's surface.

84
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:29,250
Lean slightly forward.

85
00:04:30,463 --> 00:04:32,400
Keep your head
above the surface of the water.

86
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,520
Press your chin
against the water surface.

87
00:04:35,010 --> 00:04:36,170
Look at their demonstration.

88
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:39,650
♪When I speak with the sky♪

89
00:04:42,010 --> 00:04:44,690
Yi Nanwang and Ye Haiyang,
practice underwater.

90
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:49,170
♪If you can't see the end♪

91
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:53,550
♪Do you still dare depart?♪

92
